# WindowTiler

A developer convenience feature that automatcally tiles the launched windows when working from editor.

Some features may not work depending on your desktop enviroment or Godot version.

![Window Tiler](../assets/window-tiler.gif)


## Configuration

*Auto Tile Windows* Enables auto tiling from editor launches.

*Screen* Which screen number to move and tile the windows to.

*Borderless* Enable borderless mode to make the most out of the screen real estate.



